{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdf_tutorials/pullrequests/35/comments/118380605.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/sdf_tutorials/diff/osrf/sdf_tutorials:ffa02ad368d2..e3c24ab908ee?path=pose_frame_semantics%2Fproposal.md"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdf_tutorials/pull-requests/35/_/diff#comment-118380605"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 35, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdf_tutorials/pullrequests/35.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdf_tutorials/pull-requests/35"}}, "title": "Update pose frame proposal to support //xyz[@expressed_in]"}, "content": {"raw": "Can we address that `__model__` cannot be used in `//model/pose[@relative_to]`? Also, can the implicit model frame be referred to by its name if the referring entity is at the same level as the model? For example, is the following allowed?\n\n```\n\n<world name='w'>\n  <model name='M1'/>\n  <model name='M2'>\n    <pose relative_to='M1'>1 0 0 0 0 0</pose>\n  </model>\n</world>\n```\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Can we address that <code>__model__</code> cannot be used in <code>//model/pose[@relative_to]</code>? Also, can the implicit model frame be referred to by its name if the referring entity is at the same level as the model? For example, is the following allowed?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">&lt;world</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&#39;w&#39;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;model</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&#39;M1&#39;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;model</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&#39;M2&#39;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;pose</span> <span class=\"na\">relative_to=</span><span class=\"s\">&#39;M1&#39;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>1 0 0 0 0 0<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/pose&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/model&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/world&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-09-25T23:02:35.160995+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Addisu Z. Taddese", "uuid": "{9d7fdc68-d270-4080-bf03-4df0d0dbf635}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B9d7fdc68-d270-4080-bf03-4df0d0dbf635%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B9d7fdc68-d270-4080-bf03-4df0d0dbf635%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:90bc87b0-2886-4377-a17c-3a6629a697ff/afbf9be5-1e4c-4810-89d4-e58831f34b11/128"}}, "nickname": "azeey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:90bc87b0-2886-4377-a17c-3a6629a697ff"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": 159, "outdated": true, "path": "pose_frame_semantics/proposal.md"}, "updated_on": "2019-09-25T23:02:35.171044+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 118380605}